    value: "```wing\nstatic sleep: (delay: duration): void\n```\n---\nSuspends execution for a given duration.\n### Parameters\n- `delay` ‚Äî `duration` ‚Äî The time to suspend execution.\n\n*@inflightImpl* *__sleep__inflight*"
  sortText: ff|sleep
  insertText: sleep($1)
