    value: "```wing\nstatic tryEnv: (name: str): str?\n```\n---\nReturns the value of an environment variable.\n### Parameters\n- `name` ‚Äî `str` ‚Äî The name of the environment variable.\n\n### Returns\nThe value of the environment variable or `nil`.\n\n### Remarks\nReturns `nil` if not found or empty."
