- label: ulid
  kind: 2
  detail: "(options: UlidOptions?): str"
  documentation:
    kind: markdown
    value: "```wing\nstatic ulid: (options: UlidOptions?): str\n```\n---\nGenerates universally unique lexicographically sortable identifier.\n### Parameters\n- `...options` ‚Äî `UlidOptions?` ‚Äî - Optional options object for generating the ID.\n  \n  - `seed?` ‚Äî `num?` ‚Äî You can also input a seed time which will consistently give you the same string for the time component.\n\n### Remarks\n#\n\n*@link* *https://github.com/ulid/javascript*"
  sortText: ff|ulid
  insertText: ulid($1)
  insertTextFormat: 2
  command:
    title: triggerParameterHints
    command: editor.action.triggerParameterHints
